					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">There's also software blitting to modify background tiles around the player to add white and black to the other three colors, but that's very slow.  You'd need to reserve Black and White in your background palettes as well, leaving two remaining colors in each background palette.<br /><br />Or even sprite overlays, if you need to add a small black and white object (8px wide) to another object.  Mario 2 does that.</div>

					
