				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Another interesting trick is that you can cycle palettes on certain items, projectiles, effects or anything that shines/flashes/glows, and it won't look like they're reusing palettes from other objects. SMB1 does this a lot, but the effect looks cooler in Batman Return of the Joker. As long as the palettes have their colors sorted by brightness, the exact colors used may not even matter much.</div>

